{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"43a2bb3b3e","title":"中共中央关于南京大字报问题的电话通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"34b97d9636","index":0,"year":1976,"month":4,"day":1,"articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"吴德","id":"7f0393737e","type":"人物"},{"name":"中共中央通知","id":"91736a0628","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"异端思潮","id":"ca0e96a612","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第27册 “文化大革命”参考资料 下册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"558fd04d5e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席已圈阅","index":0,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfd02c485d","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央关于南京大字报","index":1,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f56eb6839b","type":"paragraph","text":"问题的电话通知","index":2,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f407200004","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七六年四月一日）","index":3,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3955fe0ea5","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）据了解，最近几天，南京出现了矛头指向中央领导同志的大字报、大标语，这是分裂以毛主席为首的党中央，转移批邓大方向的政治事件。你们必须立即采取有效措施，全部复盖这类大字报、大标语。对有关群众要做好思想工作。要警惕别有用心的人借机扩大事态，进行捡乱、破坏。","index":4,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4701f7677f","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）对这次政治事件的幕后策划人，要彻底追查（）所谓总理遗言，完全是反革命谣言，必须辟谣，并追查谣言制遗者。（四）任何人不准冲击铁路","index":5,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"251e7f87bd","type":"paragraph","text":"吴德在天安门广场广播讲话","index":6,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30d8718aac","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七六年四月五日）同志们！","index":7,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"55fdf7cba6","type":"paragraph","text":"近几天来，正当我们学习伟大领袖毛主席的重要指示，反击右倾翻案风，抓革命、促牛产之际，极少数别有用心的坏人利用清明节，蓄意制造政治事件，把矛头直接指向毛主席，指向党中央，安图扭转批判不肯改悔的走资派邓小平的修正主义路线，反击右倾翻案风的大方向。我们要认清这-政治事件的反动性，穿他们的阴谋施计，提高革命警惕，不要上当。","index":8,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52f8795235","type":"paragraph","text":"全市广大革命群众和革命干部，要以阶级斗争为纲，立即行动起来，以实际行动保卫毛主席，保卫党中央，保卫毛主席的无产阶级革命路线，保卫我们社会主义祖国的伟大首都坚决打击反革命破坏活动，进一步加强和巩固无产阶级专政，发展大好形势。让我们团结在以毛主席为首的党中央周围，争取更大的胜利","index":9,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"377ed52964","type":"paragraph","text":"今天，在天安门广场有坏人进行破坏揭乱，进行反革命破坏活动，革命群众应立即离开广场，不要受他们的蒙蔽。","index":10,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5490ea0b60","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社1976年4月7讯，载4月8F《人民门报》","index":11,"publicationId":"0b2f26ed-ad29-48e7-9c89-446932a97ab0","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":429,"end":429}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"68bbb8f2c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）所谓总理遗言，完全是反革命谣言，必须辟谣，并追查谣言制造者。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"702f82a356","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）任何人不准冲击铁路。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71596ed191","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席已圈阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7868e659a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）据了解，最近几天，南京出现了矛头指向中央领导同志的大字报、大标语，这是分裂以毛主席为首的党中央，转移批邓大方向的政治事件。你们必须立即采取有效措施，全部覆盖这类大字报、大标语。对有关群众要做好思想工作，要警惕别有用心的人借机扩大事态，进行捣乱，破坏。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0b9d73e34","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）对这次政治事件的幕后策划人，要彻底追查。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f50baf89bf","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于南京大字报问题的电话通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}